          </ul>
          <a href="next" class="next"><img class="next-icon" src="{{'link-arrow-orange.png' | asset_url}}" alt=""></a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third text-wrapper">
          <h3>Recap of freshman anatomy:</h3>
          <p>Fresh blood delivers oxygen to your muscles. Old blood strips away metabolic waste (like lactic acid) that weighs them down. Compression speeds this process up, and keeps your muscles working at peak condition longer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="grid__item centered no-padding">
      {{ pages.compression-101-tighter.content }}
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item centered no-padding">
      
      <div class="tile-wrapper infographic goldilocks-infographic">
        <div class="grid__item large--two-thirds large--right medium--two-thirds medium--right slider goldilocks-slider">
          <a href="prev" class="prev"><img class="prev-icon" src="{{ 'link-arrow-black-reverse.png' | asset_url }}" alt=""></a>
          <ul class="slides grid">
          <li class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <img class="goldilocks-img" src="{{ 'too-loose.png' | asset_url }}" alt="">
                <div class="text-wrapper text">
                  <h6>Too loose</h6>
                  <h6>Underperforms</h6>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <img class="goldilocks-img" src="{{ 'just-right.png' | asset_url }}" alt="">
                <div class="text-wrapper text">
                  <h6>Just right</h6>
                  <h6>Perfectly balanced</h6>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <img class="goldilocks-img" src="{{ 'too-tight.png' | asset_url }}" alt="">
                <div class="text-wrapper text">
                  <h6>Too tight</h6>
                  <h6>Overcompensates</h6>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="next" class="next"><img class="next-icon" src="{{ 'link-arrow-black.png' | asset_url }}" alt=""></a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid__item large--one-third medium--one-third text-wrapper">
          <h3>The Goldilocks Effect</h3>
          <p>Too tight and compression cuts off the return of fresh blood. Too loose and it won't send blood back to the heart any faster. In short: compression should massage your muscles, not strangle them.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="grid__item centered no-padding">
      {{ pages.compression-101-measurement.content }}
    </div>

    <div class="grid__item centered no-padding">
