          </div>
          <div class="grid__item large--one-half large--right medium--one-half medium--right text-wrapper">
            <h3>Easy as 1-2-3</h3>
            <p>Three measurements. That's all it takes to go from off-the-shelf compression to medical graduated compression that's tailored to the exact size and shape of your muscles.</p>
            <p><span>No measuring tape?</span><br> We can help you measure with a dollar bill and headphone cord.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

